OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FThe Ministry of Defence confirmed the
OL,8,Faircraft carrier is being readied for
OL,9,Fdeployment, but no decisions have been
OL,10,Fmade. ITV News Reporter Ellie Pitt has
OL,11,Fthe details
OL,13,FPreparations to deploy the aircraft
OL,14,Fcarrier HMS Prince of Wales, one of
OL,15,FBritain's two aircraft carriers, are
OL,16,Fbeing stepped up in response to the
OL,17,FMiddle East war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FNo decisions have been made to deploy
OL,8,Fthe aircraft carrier, ITV News has
OL,9,Fbeen told, but work is being carried
OL,10,Fout to increase its readiness. This
OL,11,Fmeans it could be deployed more
OL,12,Fquickly if a decision is made to
OL,13,Fmobilise it to the region.
OL,15,FThe work being carried out does not
OL,16,Fpreclude it from undertaking other
OL,17,Fplanned missions, and the Ministry of
OL,18,FDefence (MoD) says it has "always been
OL,19,Fon very high readiness".
OL,26,@zD@[OU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FIt's understood that the warship,
OL,8,Fwhich is in Portsmouth receiving
OL,9,Froutine maintenance, is now at five
OL,10,Fdays' notice to sail, down from ten.
OL,12,FA Ministry of Defence spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid it is "increasing the
OL,14,Fpreparedness of the carrier".
OL,16,FHere, ITV News looks at what this
OL,17,Fmeans and what the HMS Prince of Wales
OL,18,Fcould bring to the fight in the Middle
OL,19,FEast.
OL,21,FWhat is the HMS Prince of Wales?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FIt is one of the UK's largest and most
OL,8,Fadvanced warships.
OL,10,FAlongside the HMS Queen Elizabeth, the
OL,11,Ftwo make up the Queen Elizabeth Class
OL,12,F- the most powerful vessels ever
OL,13,Fconstructed for the Royal Navy.
OL,15,FThey each weigh 65,000 tonnes, have a
OL,16,Ftop speed in excess of 25 knots per
OL,17,Fhour and a range of 10,000 nautical
OL,18,Fmiles.
OL,20,FThe flight deck is 280 metres long and
OL,21,F70 metres wide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FWhat can it carry?
OL,9,FIt can carry up to 72 aircraft,
OL,10,Fincluding a maximum of 36 F-35B
OL,11,Ffighter jets.
OL,13,FTwo lifts are capable of lifting four
OL,14,FF-35 fighter jets from the hangar to
OL,15,Fthe flight deck in 60 seconds.
OL,17,FCrew and weaponry
OL,19,FHMS Prince of Wales can operate on a
OL,20,Fcrew of 678, but can accommodate up to
OL,21,F1,600 people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
