PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FIt uses three Phalanx CIWS (close-in
OL,8,Fweapon system) turrets to deal with
OL,9,Fincoming threats from the sea and air.
OL,11,FThe Phalanx has a dual fire rate of
OL,12,F3,000 or 4,500 shots per minute and is
OL,13,Fcapable of hitting targets up to a
OL,14,Fmile away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
