FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FHMS Prince of Wales' crew will have an
OL,8,Fexpansive range of skills, and will be
OL,9,Fable to meet a range of tasks around
OL,10,Fthe world, including: fighting
OL,11,Fterrorism, high intensity warfighting
OL,12,Fand humanitarian relief, according to
OL,13,Fthe Royal Navy.
OL,15,FHow is the UK involved in the US-
OL,16,FIsrael war with Iran?
OL,18,FThe UK is allowing the US to use
OL,19,FBritish bases for "defensive actions".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
