OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FA first 146ft B-1 Lancer arrived at
OL,8,FRAF Fairford in Gloucestershire on
OL,9,FFriday evening, and three more
OL,10,Ffollowed on Saturday morning.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
