PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FA Merlin helicopter is also being sent
OL,8,Fto the region to help with
OL,9,Fsurveillance from the air and RAF
OL,10,FTyphoon and F-35 jets are continuing
OL,11,Fair operations over Jordan, Qatar and
OL,12,FCyprus.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer has repeatedly
OL,15,Frefused to become involved in
OL,16,Foffensive operations in Iran and has
OL,17,Fsaid that the UK is not taking part in
OL,18,Fthe US-Israeli strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
