PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FBritain has been criticised by allies
OL,8,Fover its response to the Middle East
OL,9,Fcrisis, particularly over the defence
OL,10,Fof Cyprus, where a UK base was struck
OL,11,Fby a drone earlier this week.
OL,13,FHMS Dragon, a Type 45 warship, will
OL,14,Fdepart in the next few days to begin
OL,15,Fits mission to defend the base from
OL,16,Fattacks by Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,FIn a statement, the MoD said: "We have
OL,8,Fbeen bolstering our UK military
OL,9,Fpresence in the Middle East since
OL,10,FJanuary, and we have already deployed
OL,11,Fcapabilities to protect British people
OL,12,Fand our allies in the region,
OL,13,Fincluding Typhoons, F-35 jets, air
OL,14,Fdefence systems and an extra 400
OL,15,Fpersonnel into Cyprus.
OL,26,@oD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772986287
OL,3,CUK readies HMS Prince of Wales amid
OL,4,CMiddle East crisis - what you need to
OL,5,Cknow
OL,7,F"Since the strikes began, we've had
OL,8,FBritish jets in the sky shooting down
OL,9,Fdrowns and have sent additional assets
OL,10,Fto the region to further reinforce our
OL,11,Fair defences, including more Typhoons
OL,12,Fand Wildcat helicopters with drone
OL,13,Fbusting missiles.
OL,15,F"HMS Prince of Wales has always been
OL,16,Fon very high readiness and we are
OL,17,Fincreasing the preparedness of the
OL,18,Fcarrier, reducing the time it would
OL,19,Ftake to set sail for any deployment."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
